/usr/local/sbin/ovpn-resolvconf
# VPN_SWITCH_RESOLVCONF_openvpn - OpenVPN resolvconf script base path
#
# Used for DNS management in phase-based connect/disconnect scripts.
# This follows the VPN_SWITCH_RESOLVCONF_<protocol> naming convention for
# protocol-agnostic resolvconf script lookup.
#
# Default: /usr/local/sbin/ovpn-resolvconf
# Script automatically appends -up or -down:
#   - Connect calls: /usr/local/sbin/ovpn-resolvconf-up
#   - Disconnect calls: /usr/local/sbin/ovpn-resolvconf-down
#
# Used by:
#   - Phase scripts: template/phase/openvpn/connect/dns.sh
#   - Phase scripts: template/phase/openvpn/disconnect/dns.sh
